# WASH Survey Raw Data for Dhaka, Bangladesh

WASH survey raw data collected by WSUP in Dhaka, Bangladesh

## Usage

``` r
surveyDataBGD
```

## Format

A data frame with 217 variables and 1282 entries:

  Country

- `ccode`:

  Country Code

- `zone`:

  Enumeration Area

- `type`:

  Sampling Point Type

  Quadrat Number

  Household ID

  Month of Survey
